# Cursor AI Instructions for this project

# Python coding standards
- Use Python 3.x syntax and best practices
- Follow PEP 8 style guidelines
- Add type hints where appropriate
- Include docstrings for functions and classes

# Project-specific rules
- This is a Raspberry Pi hexapod robot control project
- Server code is in the Server/ directory
- Client code is in the Client/ directory
- Use FastAPI for REST API endpoints
- Use uvicorn as the ASGI server

# Code organization
- Keep functions modular and reusable
- Add error handling for hardware interactions
- Use descriptive variable and function names
- Comment complex logic, especially hardware control code

